pageTitle: British Pair Go Championship Results | British Go Association
textBeforeTable: Main Tournament Held in the Foxcombe Lodge Hotel, Boars Hill, near Oxford. The event was divided into two sections. The strongest eight pairs played in a tournament for which World Amateur Pair Go and European Pair Go qualification points were allocated. The other pairs played in a handicap tournament. 10 June 2012 Tournament Date:  British Pair Go Tournament Name:  British Pair Go Championship Results Content Home › Forum Notifications Enhancements needed Should we have a public membership list?
